{"tid":1547391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［831核彈？］被警犬壓頸嘅手足好可能當場就無左意識！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T17:56:03.000Z","uid":96930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71ef0b5bac507628fbc1e7aa315469f6ba5f8526","tid":1547391,"uid":96930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"係呢個post入面大家仲有啲野未留意到！！！！<br />\n[核彈] 831死亡真相<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545309</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2136822073313759/posts/2323661137963184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2136822073313759%2Fposts%2F2323661137963184&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=429379ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2136822073313759/posts/2323661137963184</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGSrunO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGSrunO.gif&h=95f9aff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係義士被狗大力壓頸係之後地鐵職員帶左個人去個個傷者嘅位置 個個人手上面拎住舊橙色野（段片2:30開始）似乎係spinal board，一般急救時用黎固定<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">脊椎/脊柱受傷嘅傷者</span></span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZH67Ydu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZH67Ydu.png&h=60eac0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9iqKTu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9iqKTu.png&h=fbd337ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係話，傷者當時好可能係出現左啲嚴重徵狀，令到啲狗要通報地鐵職員，再帶埋first aid黎去睇佢。而個塊橙色板證明當時係懷疑佢係傷到條脊椎，例如有機會係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失去意識、手腳無反應、嘔白泡</span></span>等，先會拎塊spinal board出黎用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但留意返<span style=\"color: red;\">ha secrets </span>係星期一fc完係咁樣寫的：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>Admin 向各讀者致歉<br />\n<br />\n#9026 有關太子地鐵事件究竟有冇傷者死亡.......<br />\n希望大家明白, Admin 只能check 到送左去HA 既人, 冇送過黎直接出左唔知邊度, 我地係Check 唔到. <br />\n<br />\nadmin 們check 到半夜4 點, 冇能為力啦......<br />\n<br />\n用我地方法fact check 既, 係<br />\n3個紅色: 心口痛、頭部受傷、呼吸困難<br />\n2個黃色: 頭部受傷、呼吸困難<br />\n2個綠色: 膊頭甩骹，頭暈<br />\n經地鐵運去荔枝角地鐵站先送去明愛及瑪嘉烈, 延遲醫治 3 個鐘.<br />\n<br />\n依 7 個冇死到. <br />\n<br />\n如果係現場certified dead 既case (by DH 法醫 or FSD Medical director authorized ambulance crew), 係唔會送去HA, 會送去XX 殮房. (唔係under HA, 特登唔打, 你懂的) . 醫護親戚應該唔會知既....<br />\n<br />\n原文comment 有人講到運埋條屍出公海變失蹤人口甘......<br />\n甘Admin 只係做HA, 佢玩到甘大我地真係Check 唔到. 你係Comment 係甘小我地七頭廢老都冇用.<br />\n<br />\nThese are the facts in HA.<br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中只有頭部受傷同呼吸困難，並無提到送院嘅有任何脊椎/脊柱受傷嘅徵狀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以只有兩種可能性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 當日有人出現過脊椎受傷嘅徵狀，例如失去意識，個人郁唔到、嘔白泡等，令到在場人士拎左呢塊spinal board出黎用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 當日拎呢塊板嘅人其實都唔熟情況，亂拎黎用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係如果當時係上左呢塊板，救護黎嘅時候唔會亂去郁佢，應該個人會連塊版上救護車，咁救護理應有印象有傷者係用過呢塊板並且講出黎，但到而家咁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多人爆料都係無人提過現場有脊椎/脊柱受傷嘅傷者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家只有第一手接觸嘅救護員/ 有人識得呢個義士仲在生先叫可以fact check到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd451b430a0c96376aee5061294f836c3c15e983","tid":1547391,"uid":83094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"913cc5aefd004f192ce939ce36a1391bfc90900c","tid":1547391,"uid":179276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"擔架黎 同埋唔係黎救佢"},{"pid":"240a46bb2239d14aa46ae718c18d990abad006fc","tid":1547391,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13e2197042c5af8dcaa7fd5987c01ea12e5c48ec","tid":1547391,"uid":179276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913cc5aefd004f192ce939ce36a1391bfc90900c","tid":1547391,"uid":179276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"擔架黎 同埋唔係黎救佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ten567KT16o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dten567KT16o&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=07f8c4fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ten567KT16o</a><br />\n4合1條片2:30-3:00右上應該就係蘋果影到6:40比人叫&quot;醒呀&quot;個個人<br />\n呢條片0:50-1:10睇到popo全身重量單膝隔住背囊壓頸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=715688962177125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D715688962177125&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy